law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 402, sec. 5, effective January 1, 1984. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 81, sec. 1, effective March 29, 1976. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 143, effective June 21, 1974.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Secretary of state to place candidates' names on ballots -- Provision for casting "uncommitted" vote.
